    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Attaching a drawing, print, photograph, or other work of art done on paper to a cardboard or other backing by using a thermoplastic tissue as an adhesive.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
